Number 26: Captain Scott.
4 Form questions then use text in Ex. 3 to answer them.
1 Columbs/live/in India ?
Did Columbus live in India ?
No, he didnt. He lived in Italy.
2 when/ he/ leave Europe ?
When did he leave Europe ?
He left Europe in 1492.
3 how long/ be / his first voyage ?
How long was his first voyage ?
His first voyage was for five weeks.
4 what/ he / bring back to Europe ?
What did he bring back to Europe ?
He brought back gold, cotton, birds and plants to Europe
